This is a simple version of HelloCreature Mailer for php.  

Instructions:

1) Set up your HelloCreature account at hellocreature.com

2) Click on "setup instructions" and find your API Key.

3) Require hcmailer.php in your script.

4) Substitute hellocreature_mail() for PHP's built-in mail() function.

Notes:

If you are sending HTML email, please be sure to pass in a content-type 
header.
